<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AIO-the All in One place</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/home.css">
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="images/AIO logo.png" alt="AIO-the All in One Place">
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            <h2 id="AIO-slogan">The All in One place</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/joinChatroom">AIO Bazzar</a></li>
            <li><a href="/portal2Menu">Shram Sarthi</a></li>
            <li><a href="/portal3Home">Joblens</a></li>
            <li><a href="/">About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/">Contact Us</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="hamburger">
            <div class="line"></div>
            <div class="line"></div>
            <div class="line"></div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <hr>
    <main class="main">
        <div class="heading-slogan">
            <h1>CONNECT, SHOP, WORK: SEAMELESS EMPOWERMENT IN EVERY STEP</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="intro">
            <p>Join us in revolutionizing heritage preservation by empowering daily wage workers to safeguard and
                maintain our cultural treasures while finding job opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="account-buttons">
            <button id="signup">Signup</button>
            <button id="login">Login</button>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-explore">
            <h3 onclick="scrollToElement('cards-container')">Explore our portals</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="cards-container">
            <div class="card" id="portal1">
                <img class="portals-img" src="images/portal1 svg.jpg" alt="">
                <h2>AIO Bazzar</h2>
                <div class="card-features">
                    <h4>• Purchase products directly from local shops.</h4>
                    <h4>• Immerse yourself in a curated virtual shopping space.</h4>
                    <h4>• Connect directly with local shop owners through seamless chat features.</h4>
                </div>
                <button><a href="/joinChatroom">Learn More</a></button>
            </div>

            <div class="card" id="portal2">
                <img class="portals-img" src="images/portal2 svg.jpg" alt="">
                <h2>Shram Sarthi</h2>
                <div class="card-features">
                    <h4>• Connect laborers and users; unique regional language task lists via machine.</h4>
                    <h4>• Effortlessly bring visions to life; hassle-free task management.</h4>
                    <h4>• Join united professionals; regional language support for inclusive collaboration.</h4>
                </div>
                <button><a href="/portal2Menu">Learn More</a></button>
            </div>

            <div class="card" id="portal3">
                <img class="portals-img" src="images/portal3 svg.jpg" alt="">
                <h2>Joblens</h2>
                <div class="card-features">
                    <h4>• Upload CV, find perfect job match; eliminate listing hassle.</h4>
                    <h4>• AIO's innovation ensures efficient search, aligning skills with opportunities.</h4>
                    <h4>• Elevate career journey with AIO's precise job role predictions.</h4>
                </div>
                <button><a href="/portal3Home">Learn More</a></button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="our-story">
            <div class="story-text">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>IIITN proudly introduces AIO - The All-In-One Place, a visionary platform aligned with Sustainable
                    Development Goal 8. Comprising three dynamic portals, AIO offers users the ability to create
                    e-commerce sites and engage in community discussions. Shram Sarthi stands out as the heart of our
                    mission, connecting skilled laborers directly with those in need, fostering collaboration and
                    teamwork through a review and bidding system. Meanwhile, Joblens leverages AI to predict job roles
                    from CVs, streamlining the job search process. AIO is more than a platform; it's a holistic
                    ecosystem, driving entrepreneurship, connecting laborers, and embracing AI for a smarter workforce,
                    all contributing to a more prosperous future.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="story-img">
                <img src="images/Our Story.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="video-tutorial">
            <h2>Watch our tutorial!</h2>
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ym9oT3UObc0?si=jgiy68MnDXyzyx3c" frameborder="0"
                allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="contact-details">
            <div class="social-handles">
                <h3>Feel free to reach out</h3>
                <div class="icons">
                    <img src="images/Icons/linkedin.png" alt="">
                    <img src="images/Icons/instagram.png" alt="">
                    <img src="images/Icons/github.png" alt="">
                    <img src="images/Icons/youtube.png" alt="">
                    <img src="images/Icons/gmail.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="js/home.js"></script>
</body>

</html>